overview: Set 1: Sample in a Jar, Free, Simple > Back on the Train, Waiting All Night, 555, Roggae, The Dogs > 46 Days Set 2: Chalk Dust Torture > Ghost > Can't Always Listen[1] > Ghost > Waves > Bathtub Gin > Mike's Song > Bouncing Around the Room > Weekapaug Groove -> What's the Use? > Weekapaug Groove Encore: Character Zero [1] Debut. Teases: · Auld Lang Syne and What's the Use? teases in Weekapaug Groove · Magilla tease in Simple Notes: This show was webcast via Live Phish and featured the debut of Can't Always Listen. Page teased Magilla in Simple. The second Weekapaug contained Auld Lang Syne and What's The Use? teases from Trey.
title: Phish 12-30-15
